        <mxCell id="note_fk" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=12;whiteSpace=wrap;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;rounded=1;spacing=10;" value="Why this solves the naming problem:&#xa;&#xa;bidding_zone / product / market / source in&#xa;prod.prices become FK columns, not free text.&#xa;&#xa;An endpoint that tries to insert &quot;day ahead&quot;&#xa;when only &quot;DAY_AHEAD&quot; exists in dim_product&#xa;fails the FK constraint at insert time.&#xa;&#xa;New codes require a deliberate row in the&#xa;dim table (reviewed, one canonical spelling) —&#xa;never an accidental typo in a parser." vertex="1">
